formThreeBId.notesToCertificate: We have relied upon the estimates given by the management in case of costs other than construction cost. The preparation of the accompanying Statement is the responsibility of the Management of the Company. This responsibility includes designing, implementing and maintaining internal control relevant to the preparation and presentation of the Statement. The certificate is addressed to and provided to the promoters of the project  solely for the purpose to enable comply with requirement of RERA , and should not be used by any other person or for any other purpose. Accordingly, we do not accept or assume any liability or any duty of care for any other purpose or to any other person to whom this certificate is shown or into whose hands it may come without our prior consent in writing. Cost of Land is considered as per the sale deed of Land. Land cost is not indexed. Areas for the units and No of parkings are taken as provided by the management. Booking Deposits received for sold inventory  and consideration for unsold inventory is taken as provided by the management and as per books of accounts as mentioned under booking deposits received. Also in case of KYC/Contact Details of the allottees the same is taken as provided by the management. The promoter has opened a separate RERA Account but the bank instead of routing funds from collection account to RERA account is directly  transferring the funds to current account, however it is only a routing lapse . We have not audited books of accounts and data is taken as provided by the management. The unit consideration is inclusive of GST and hence the amount received is also mentioned inclusive of GST. thereby the amount withdrawn shown is also inclusive of GST. Amount of secured and unsecured loan shown is inclusive of interest outstanding and paid. As informed to us by the management the project loan taken has been repaid in full as on the date of the certificate. Promoter had taken loan from DCB Bank but the whole amount of loan is repaid on the date of this certificate hence the same is not shown, the details of loan is shown in the earlier certificate issued. The incurred Construction cost of the project has increased than the estimated cost of construction hence we have restricted the withdrawal  up to the maximum allowable incurred and paid amount. Moreover Project has received BU Permission in March 2022. since the term loan on the project is repaid in full the status of the encumbrance is amended to "Released"
